Tompkins Street, north from East Houston Street. Shown under demolition are buildings Nos. 524-518 East Houston and 424-418 East 3rd Streets; on the west side of Tompkins Street, between East Houston and East 3rd Streets. After widening process, Tompkins Street will form a portion of the new East River Drive.

January 14, 1936.

P. L. Sperr.
